        },
        {
            name: "Megha Arora",
            role: "Cloud Solution Architect",
            text: "Sky States made my career change very easy. The instructors explained concepts smoothly, and the projects helped me understand how everything works in business environments.",
        },
        {
            name: "Jason Miller",
            role: "IT Operations Manager",
            text: "I joined with no technical experience and expected the learning curve to be complex. Instead, every element was structured, and the mentors were always available whenever I required guidance.",
