            role: "Security Analyst",
            text: "Cybersecurity always looked complicated until I joined Sky States. The instructors simplified every topic and encouraged practice through labs. It prepared me well for my first analyst role.",
        },
        {
            name: "Nicholas Walker",
            role: "Cyber Security Associate",
            text: "The ethical hacking labs were interactive. Instead of learning concepts, we learned how to find risks and think like security experts.",
        },
        {
            name: "Brandon Scott",
            role: "SOC Analyst",
            text: "Mock interviews and certification assistance were valuable as the technical training. The mentors genuinely wanted every learner to succeed in their career journeys.",
        },
        {
            name: "Karan Malhotra",
            role: "Information Security Executive",
            text: "I appreciated how the program maintained networking, functioning systems, and security concepts before moving into upgraded topics. It made learning manageable.",
        },
    ],
    DataScience: [
        {
            name: "Ananya Gupta",
            role: "Data Analyst",
            text: "The integration of Python, SQL, and machine learning projects helped me made a strong portfolio. I felt prepared when discussing my projects during interviews.",
        },
        {
            name: "Gaurav Sharma",
            role: "Business Inteliigence Analyst",
            text: "Every concept was supported with exercises, making even upgraded machine learning concepts easier to understand. The mentors always empowered questions.",
        },
        {
            name: "Sophia Cooper",
            role: "Machine Learning Engineer",
            text: "The curriculum covered both traditional analytics and modern AI tools, which made the learning experience very familiar. I majorly enjoyed working on real datasets.",
        },
        {
            name: "Daniel Brooks",
            role: "Data Scientist",
            text: "The instructors focused on solving business problems rather than simply teaching approaches. That practical method helped me change into a data analytics role much quicker.",
        },
    ],
};

const expertReviews = [
    {
        name: "Sarah Walker",
        role: "IT Infrastructure Manager",
        text: "Sky States gives a learning experience that depicts real workplace expectations. The programs integrate structured learning with practical execution, making them valuable for experts looking to build technical expertise.",
    },
    {
        name: "David Richardson",
        role: "Senior Systems Engineer",
        text: "I recommended Sky States to some members of my engineering team after reviewing the course module. The curriculum is proper, modern, and offers practical exposure that helps learners apply concepts in professional environments.",
    },
    {
        name: "James Collins",
        role: "Cloud Solutions Consultant",
        text: "The Cloud and DevOps training goes with current enterprise practices. From automation tools to strategies, the curriculum covers technologies organizations actively use today. It is the best platform for professionals.",
    },
    {
        name: "Emily Carter",
        role: "Cybersecurity Consultant",
        text: "I was impressed by the balance between theory and practical application. Learners complete guided labs, work on realistic projects, and receive mentorship throughout the program. That method generates technical confidence.",
    },
    {
        name: "Ethan Brown",
        role: "DevOps Architect",
        text: "Some online training providers focus only on certifications, but Sky States focuses on becoming job-ready. Portfolio projects, interview preparation, career assistance, and technical curriculum make learners better prepared for recruitment processes.",
    },
    {
        name: "Olivia Martinez",
        role: "Technology Program Manager",
        text: "Sky States combines live instruction, experienced mentors, updated learning materials, and responsive student support to create an interactive environment for both freshers and professionals.",
    },
